snippet.title: Above Snakes - Official Open Alpha Week Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Here's another look at Above Snakes, including crafting elements and more. Create the world by placing isometric tiles in this upcoming survival base-building PC game. The Above Snakes' open Alpha week runs from June 13 to June 20.
